ok argues that the more we understand how people felt in fosterage, the more we understand medieval Ireland.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aEmotionsxSocial aspectszIrelandxHistory. 0aFoster childrenzIrelandxHistoryyTo 1500. 0aFoster home carezIrelandxHistoryyTo 1500. 4aAnthropology. 4aCentral Middle Ages. 4aEarly Middle Ages. 4aHistory. 4aSociology and Social History. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Ireland.2bisacsh  aHistory of childhood.  aIrish literature.  ahistory of emotions.  amedieval Ireland.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311068955608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishz978311070473008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2020z9783110704525oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP ROW Ebook Package English 2020z978311069630140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048541973zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048541973423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9789048541973.jpg  a978-3-11-068955-6  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-069629-5  DG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2b2020  a978-3-11-069630-1  PP ROW Ebook Package English 2020b2020  a978-3-11-070471-6  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishb2020  a978-3-11-070473-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2020 Englishb2020  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL 